## 6) Plan output JSON schema

Name: `GymPersonalizedPlan`

Minimum requirements:

* `program` with title/summary/time budget/disclaimer
* `insights[3..5]`
* `days[7]`, each day with:

  * `day_number` 1..7
  * `is_locked` default true for 2..7 (app can override lock based on premium)
  * `objective` string
  * `workout.steps[3..8]`
  * `guided_session` with script blocks totaling ~90‚Äì240 seconds
  * `fallback`

(Use the schema previously agreed, or keep it in `schemas/plan-output.json`.)

