## 8) LLM prompt (reliable structured JSON)

### System prompt

* Role: planning engine
* Output: JSON only
* Rules:

  * match time budget
  * plan is ‚Äúself-development/mental gym‚Äù not clinical therapy
  * no guaranteed results

### User prompt template

Provide schema instructions and input JSON:

* must return 7 days
* guided session script blocks sum to ~2‚Äì3 minutes
* day 1 unlocked, days 2‚Äì7 locked by default

### Reliability measures

* Use low temperature (0.2‚Äì0.4)
* If JSON parse fails:

  * re-ask: ‚ÄúReturn valid JSON only. Fix syntax.‚Äù
* Optional: JSON schema validation on server to enforce shape.

